      "line": 29,
      "message": "Is it possible to give a default value for RUNTIME_NAME by adding this above the appender:\n\n    <property name=\"RUNTIME_NAME\" value=\"${RUNTIME_NAME:-acm-runtime}\" />\n\nAlternatively, we could make the entire staticParameters optional & configurable if we want more flexibility:\n\n    <property name=\"LOGBACK_STATIC_PARAMS\" value=\"${LOGBACK_STATIC_PARAMS:-}\" />\n    <appender name=\"STDOUT\" class=\"ch.qos.logback.core.ConsoleAppender\">\n        <encoder class=\"ch.qos.logback.core.encoder.LayoutWrappingEncoder\">\n            <layout class=\"org.onap.policy.clamp.acm.runtime.config.LoggingConsoleLayout\">\n                <timestampFormat>yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm:ss.SSS+00:00</timestampFormat>\n                <timestampFormatTimezoneId>${TIMEZONE}</timestampFormatTimezoneId>\n                <staticParameters>${LOGBACK_STATIC_PARAMS}</staticParameters>",
